definition: Czech/Czech Republic/abbr. for 捷克[Jie2 ke4]
to attain/to reach/to amount to/to communicate/eminent

pinyin: Jie2 da2 Hang2 kong1 Huo4 yun4

sentences.english: But Jetta A2 and Santana B2 are still in production even today.
sentences.chinese: 但是直至今日捷達和桑塔納還是在產。

sentences.english: High- carbon microalloyed engine connecting rods for Jetta car were prepared by controlling steel metallurgy, forging process and cooling process.
sentences.chinese: 用高碳微合金非調質鋼試製了捷達轎車發動機連桿。

sentences.english: The only German car I owned was a VW Jetta Diesel.
sentences.chinese: 我唯一擁有的一輛德國車是大衆捷達柴油車。

sentences.english: The pink slip to what? The Jetta?
Previously, all Jettas came with the 5-cylinder engine.
sentences.chinese: 以前，所有捷達帶有5缸發動機。

sentences.english: He asked an experienced driver to test-drive that Jetta for him.
sentences.chinese: 他請一位有經驗的司機爲他試開那輛捷達車。

sentences.english: The ignition system used on JETTA is controlled by computer without distributor.
sentences.chinese: 捷達王轎車採用的是無分電器微機控制點火系統。

definition: to return something to its rightful owner
lit. to lead away a goat while passing by (idiom)/fig. to opportunistically pocket sb's possessions and walk off
to postpone one's graduation (e.g. by undertaking additional studies) (abbr. for 延後畢業|延后毕业[yan2 hou4 bi4 ye4])
lit. to give medicine to a dead horse (idiom)/fig. to keep trying everything in a desperate situation
pinyin: si3 ma3 dang4 huo2 ma3 yi1

definition: lit. to directly attack Huanglong/fig. to directly combat the root of a problem
